												<td align="left" bgcolor="#ffffff" valign="top" width="25">&nbsp;</td>
												<td align="left" bgcolor="#ffffff" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 120px;" valign="top" width="542">
												<p style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3999996185303px; line-height: 18px;"><span style="display: none;">&nbsp;</span></p>

												<p style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3999996185303px; line-height: 18px;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><font color="#000000"><span style="line-height: normal;">Dear {!Step_Forward_Activity__c.Associate__c},</span></font></span></span></p>

												<p><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><font color="#000000"><span style="line-height: normal;">Thank </span></font><span style="line-height: normal;">you for applying to Step Forward. &nbsp;You have taken the first step towards securing your future and gaining 12 months of invaluable paid employment.&nbsp;We</span><font color="#000000"><span style="line-height: normal;"> are pleased to tell you that you have been successful in your application&nbsp;and we would like to invite you to the first stage of our assessment event. &nbsp;</span></font></span></span></p>

												<p><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">We were very impressed with your application&nbsp;so congratulations on reaching this stage!&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><font color="#000000"><span style="line-height: normal;">The assessment event is an opportunity for us to get to know each other better and find out if Step Forward&nbsp;is the right programme for you.&nbsp; The details of your assessment are as follows:</span></font></span></span></p>

												<p style="text-align: center;"><strong style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; text-align: center; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Date: Friday 3rd July 2015<br />
												Time: 15:55 - 19:00<br />
												Please arrive: 15:40</strong></p>

												<p><br />
												<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><font color="#000000"><span style="line-height: normal;">Please confirm your attendance <a href="http://survey.clicktools.com/go?iv=3o1k04g3pd3w3&amp;q1={!Step_Forward_Activity__c.Id}">here</a>&nbsp;<strong>by Monday 28th June.</strong></span></font></span><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><font color="#000000"><span style="line-height: normal;">&nbsp; If you do not confirm your attendance by the deadline we cannot guarantee that we can save you a space.</span></font></span><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><font color="#000000"><span style="line-height: normal;">Address:</span></font></span></span><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><font color="#000000"><span style="line-height: normal;">&nbsp;<a href="https://www.google.co.uk/maps/place/Union+Jack+Club/@51.503299,-0.110251,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m2!3m1!1s0x487604ba1b0d9c23:0x65f48d88dfcc79f1?hl=en">Union Jack Club, Sandell Street, London, SE1 8UJ</a></span></font></span></span></p>

												<p><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><font color="#000000"><span style="line-height: normal;"><strong>Stage two of the assessment will be take place&nbsp;on <span style="background-color:#FFFF00;">Saturday 21&nbsp;and Sunday 22 February</span> so please keep these dates free.&nbsp;</strong></span></font></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal;">We will send another email by Friday 13</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal;">&nbsp;February</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal;">&nbsp;with more detailed information about the assessment and tips on how to be successful.</span></p>

												<p><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><font color="#000000"><span style="line-height: normal;">If you </span></font><span style="color:#000000;"><span style="line-height: normal;">have any queries in the meantime please contact step.forward@the-challenge.org&nbsp;with &lsquo;Ste</span></span><font color="#000000"><span style="line-height: normal;">p Forward Assessment&rsquo; in the subject title or call 0203 542 2400.</span></font></span></span></p>

												<p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Well done once again for reaching this stage, we look forward to meeting you</span></span>.</span></font></p>

												<p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="line-height: normal;">----------------------------------------------------</span></font></p>

												<p><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><font color="#000000"><span style="line-height: normal;">Important information about the assessment:</span></font></span></span></p>

												<p><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><font color="#000000"><span style="line-height: normal;"><strong>Stage 1:</strong> Friday 3rd July</span></font></span></span></p>

												<p><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><font color="#000000"><span style="line-height: normal;">- Teamwork activities</span></font></span></span></p>

												<p><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><font color="#000000"><span style="line-height: normal;">- Pathway activities</span></font></span></span></p>

												<p><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><font color="#000000"><span style="line-height: normal;">We will send details of&nbsp;Stage 2 in an&nbsp;email by <span style="background-color:#FFFF00;">Friday 13 February. &nbsp;Please note the address for Stage 2 will be&nbsp;different.</span></span></font></span></span></p>

												<p><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><font color="#000000"><span style="line-height: normal;"><strong>Stage 2: </strong>&nbsp; <span style="background-color:#FFFF00;">Saturday 21 </span><strong><span style="background-color:#FFFF00;">or</span></strong><span style="background-color:#FFFF00;"> Sunday 22 February</span>&nbsp;</span></font></span></span></p>

												<p><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><font color="#000000"><span style="line-height: normal;">-</span></font></span></span><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><font color="#000000"><span style="line-height: normal;"> Individual interviews</span></font></span></p>

												<p><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><font color="#000000"><span style="line-height: normal;">Best wishes,</span></font></span></p>

												<p><span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><font color="#000000"><span style="line-height: normal;">The Step Forward Team</span></font></span></p>
